 8s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:5.7s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:3px;height:3px;top:82%;left:4%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.08;animation:float 5s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:6s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:1px;height:1px;top:9%;left:27%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.13;animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:6.3s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:2px;height:2px;top:26%;left:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.18;animation:float 7s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:6.6s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:3px;height:3px;top:43%;left:73%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.23000000000000004;animation:float 8s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:6.8999999999999995s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:1px;height:1px;top:60%;left:96%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.28;animation:float 5s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:7.199999999999999s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:2px;height:2px;top:77%;left:25%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.08;animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:7.5s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:3px;height:3px;top:94%;left:48%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.13;animation:float 7s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:7.8s\"></span><span class=\"absolute rounded-full\" style=\"width:1px;height:1px;top:21%;left:71%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);opacity:0.18;animation:float 8s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:8.1s\"></span></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center gap-6\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] backdrop-blur-sm\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:rgb(191,219,254);opacity:0;transform:translateY(-10px)\"><span class=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\"><span class=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-teal-400 opacity-60\"></span><span class=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-teal-400\"></span></span>Now building — Join the early access list</div><h1 class=\"mt-2\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-instrument-serif);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(52px, 7.5vw, 84px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#ffffff;opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\">Master <span style=\"color:rgb(96,165,250);font-style:italic\">Physics Fundamentals</span><br/>Through Interactive Learning</h1><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(15px, 1.2vw, 17px);line-height:1.65;color:rgb(191,219,254);max-width:580px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">From<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgb(96,165,250)\">Newton&#x27;s laws</span> <!-- -->and<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgb(96,165,250)\">energy conservation</span> <!-- -->to<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgb(96,165,250)\">transverse waves</span> <!-- -->and quantum mechanics — a free, comprehensive physics education platform built to make every concept click.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 items-center mt-2\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)\"><a id=\"hero-get-early-access\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-200 hover:brightness-110\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;background:#f59e0b;color:#0a0f1e;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(245,158,11,0.25)\" href=\"/#simulations\">Get Early Access<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:16px;height:16px\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a id=\"hero-browse-articles\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);color:#ffffff;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18)\" href=\"/#features\">Browse Articles</a></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;font-size:13px;color:rgb(100,116,139);opacity:0\">Trusted by<!-- --> <span style=\"font-weight:600;color:rgb(148,163,184)\">500+</span> <!-- -->students already on the list</p></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"py-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 flex flex-col items-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-size:14px;color:rgb(59, 130, 246)\">Core Concepts</span><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-[clamp(40px,5vw,60px)] leading-[1.1] text-slate-900\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-instrument-serif);font-weight:400;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">The laws that run our universe</h2><p class=\"max-w-[700px] text-lg leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(51, 65, 85)\">Physics fundamentals are precise descriptions of how every force and matter exists, moves, and interacts. Every branch of science and engineering builds on these foundations.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"group bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"h-[200px] bg-[#f8fafc] w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 border-b border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><rect x=\"75\" y=\"40\" width=\"50\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#e2e8f0\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M125 60 L165 60\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-amber)\"></path><path d=\"M75 60 L35 60\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-amber)\"></path><path d=\"M100 40 L100 15\" stroke=\"#3b82f6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-blue)\"></path><defs><marker id=\"arrow-amber\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"8\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"><path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"></path></marker><marker id=\"arrow-blue\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"8\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"><path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"></path></marker></defs></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-full text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 self-start\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">CLASSICAL MECHANICS</div><h3 class=\"text-xl mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Newton&#x27;s Laws of Motion</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Detailed explanation of exactly how every force and interaction works, starting from first classical mechanics principles to predict rocket trajectories.</p><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors group/link mt-auto w-fit\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:500;font-size:15px\" href=\"#\">Read the guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover/link:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"h-[200px] bg-[#f8fafc] w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 border-b border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M20 50 Q 50 10, 80 50 T 140 50 T 200 50\" stroke=\"#3b82f6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"transparent\"></path><path d=\"M20 50 L 200 50\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\"></path><path d=\"M80 50 L 140 50\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-green)\" marker-start=\"url(#arrow-green-start)\"></path><text x=\"110\" y=\"45\" fill=\"#22c55e\" font-size=\"10\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">λ</text><defs><marker id=\"arrow-green\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"8\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#22c55e\"></path></marker><marker id=\"arrow-green-start\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"2\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"><path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#22c55e\"></path></marker></defs></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-full text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 self-start\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">WAVES &amp; OPTICS</div><h3 class=\"text-xl mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Transverse Waves Explained</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Definition, labeled diagram, wavelength, amplitude, frequency, polarization — with real examples from light to guitar strings. 6,800 words.</p><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors group/link mt-auto w-fit\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:500;font-size:15px\" href=\"#\">Read the guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover/link:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"h-[200px] bg-[#f8fafc] w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 border-b border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"50\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"></circle><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"></circle><circle cx=\"150\" cy=\"50\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#f59e0b\"></circle><path d=\"M100 50 L50 50\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\"></path><path d=\"M100 50 L150 50\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\"></path><text x=\"100\" y=\"30\" fill=\"#3b82f6\" font-size=\"10\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">KE</text><text x=\"50\" y=\"30\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" font-size=\"10\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">PE</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"30\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" font-size=\"10\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">PE</text></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-full text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 self-start\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">THERMODYNAMICS</div><h3 class=\"text-xl mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">What Is Energy?</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Kinetic, potential, and thermal energy explained. The conservation of energy law and why it is the most important principle in all of physics.</p><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors group/link mt-auto w-fit\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:500;font-size:15px\" href=\"#\">Read the guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover/link:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"h-[200px] bg-[#f8fafc] w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 border-b border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M 20 80 Q 100 0, 180 80\" stroke=\"#3b82f6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"transparent\"></path><path d=\"M 20 80 L 180 80\" stroke=\"#94a3b8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\"></path><circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"80\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#3b82f6\"></circle><path d=\"M 20 80 L 60 40\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-amber)\"></path><path d=\"M 100 80 L 100 40\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2 2\"></path><text x=\"100\" y=\"35\" fill=\"#ef4444\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">H</text><text x=\"35\" y=\"50\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">V₀</text><text x=\"45\" y=\"75\" fill=\"#10b981\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">θ</text></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-full text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 self-start\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">CLASSICAL MECHANICS</div><h3 class=\"text-xl mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Projectile Motion</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Range, max height, time of flight equations with full worked examples. Why 45° maximises range and common exam mistakes corrected.</p><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors group/link mt-auto w-fit\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:500;font-size:15px\" href=\"#\">Read the guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover/link:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"h-[200px] bg-[#f8fafc] w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 border-b border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><text x=\"100\" y=\"35\" fill=\"#0f172a\" font-size=\"20\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"var(--font-dm-sans)\">v = fλ</text><rect x=\"30\" y=\"50\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#eff6ff\" stroke=\"#3b82f6\" stroke-width=\"1\"></rect><text x=\"50\" y=\"64\" fill=\"#3b82f6\" font-size=\"12\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">v</text><rect x=\"80\" y=\"50\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#fef3c7\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"1\"></rect><text x=\"100\" y=\"64\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" font-size=\"12\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">f</text><rect x=\"130\" y=\"50\" width=\"40\" height=\"20\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#dcfce7\" stroke=\"#22c55e\" stroke-width=\"1\"></rect><text x=\"150\" y=\"64\" fill=\"#22c55e\" font-size=\"12\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">λ</text><text x=\"50\" y=\"85\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">speed</text><text x=\"100\" y=\"85\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">frequency</text><text x=\"150\" y=\"85\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\">wavelength</text></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-full text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 self-start\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">WAVES &amp; OPTICS</div><h3 class=\"text-xl mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Wave Speed, Frequency &amp; Wavelength</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">The universal wave equation v = fλ explained from first principles. From sound waves to light — worked examples and Doppler effect.</p><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors group/link mt-auto w-fit\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:500;font-size:15px\" href=\"#\">Read the guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover/link:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"h-[200px] bg-[#f8fafc] w-full flex items-center justify-center p-6 border-b border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden\"><svg class=\"w-full h-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><text x=\"60\" y=\"20\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"1\">BEFORE</text><text x=\"140\" y=\"20\" fill=\"#94a3b8\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"1\">AFTER</text><circle cx=\"30\" cy=\"50\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#60a5fa\"></circle><circle cx=\"65\" cy=\"50\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#818cf8\"></circle><circle cx=\"130\" cy=\"50\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#a78bfa\" opacity=\"0.6\"></circle><path d=\"M 45 50 L 55 50\" stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-amber)\"></path><path d=\"M 150 50 L 170 50\" stroke=\"#10b981\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-green)\"></path><path d=\"M 90 50 L 105 50\" stroke=\"#cbd5e1\" stroke-width=\"1\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow-gray)\"></path><text x=\"100\" y=\"80\" fill=\"#0f172a\" font-size=\"8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"bold\">p₁ + p₂ = p₁&#x27; + p₂&#x27;</text><text x=\"100\" y=\"90\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-size=\"7\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Total momentum is conserved</text><defs><marker id=\"arrow-gray\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"8\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" fill=\"#cbd5e1\"></path></marker></defs></svg></div><div class=\"p-8 flex flex-col flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#eff6ff] rounded-full text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-4 self-start\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">CLASSICAL MECHANICS</div><h3 class=\"text-xl mb-3\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Conservation of Momentum</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">The principle behind every collision. Elastic vs inelastic collisions, centre of mass, worked examples, and why momentum never disappears.</p><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors group/link mt-auto w-fit\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:500;font-size:15px\" href=\"#\">Read the guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover/link:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-14 flex justify-center\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 bg-transparent hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 font-medium text-[16px] group\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"/blog\">Browse all physics articles<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section id=\"why\" class=\"py-24 relative\" style=\"background-color:#f8fafc;background-image:linear-gradient(#e2e8f0 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #e2e8f0 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 flex flex-col items-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-size:14px;color:rgb(59, 130, 246)\">Why Physics Fundamentals</span><h2 class=\"mb-6 text-[clamp(40px,5vw,60px)] leading-[1.1] text-slate-900 max-w-[800px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-instrument-serif);font-weight:400;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">The physics education platform you&#x27;ve been waiting for</h2><p class=\"max-w-[800px] text-[20px] leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">More than a website — it&#x27;s a complete learning ecosystem where physics fundamentals become intuitive through interaction, not memorization.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-blue-600\"><path d=\"M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Complete Physics Curriculum</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.6]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">From classical mechanics through electromagnetism to quantum physics — every fundamental concept explained with depth and clarity by working physicists.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-blue-600\"><path d=\"M10 2v7.31M14 9.31V2M8.5 2h7M14 9.31l6.32 9.5A2 2 0 0 1 18.66 22H5.34a2 2 0 0 1-1.66-3.19L10 9.31\"></path><path d=\"M6.5 15h11\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Interactive Simulations</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.6]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Manipulate variables, observe outcomes, build intuition. Our simulations let you experiment with physics in ways a textbook never could.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-blue-600\"><path d=\"M12 20h9\"></path><path d=\"M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Practice That Builds Mastery</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.6]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Over 1,000 problems ranging from conceptual questions to multi-step calculations, each with detailed step-by-step solutions.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-blue-600\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Conceptual Understanding First</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.6]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">We don&#x27;t just hand you formulas. Every topic starts with the physical intuition — the &#x27;why&#x27; — before introducing the mathematics.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-blue-600\"><path d=\"M3 3v18h18\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Visual Explanations</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.6]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Complex ideas like vector fields, wave interference, and orbital mechanics become clear through carefully designed diagrams and animations.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"w-[45px] h-[45px] rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"text-blue-600\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-[18px] mb-4\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:600;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Free &amp; Accessible</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.6]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Quality physics education should never sit behind a paywall. Everything we build — every lesson, simulation, and problem set — is completely free.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"curriculum\" class=\"py-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16 flex flex-col items-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-size:12px;color:rgb(59, 130, 246)\">COMPREHENSIVE CURRICULUM</span><h2 class=\"mb-6 text-[clamp(40px,5vw,56px)] leading-[1.1]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-instrument-serif);font-weight:400;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Every branch of physics,<br class=\"hidden md:block\"/> explained from the ground up</h2><p class=\"max-w-[700px] text-[17px] leading-[1.7]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Our curriculum covers all physics fundamentals — from the classical mechanics of Newton to the strange world of quantum theory. Each topic is built for genuine understanding, not exam prep alone.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 lg:gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[20px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Classical Mechanics</h3><span class=\"bg-[#eff6ff] text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-[6px] shrink-0 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">LIVE</span></div><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed mt-auto\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Newton&#x27;s Laws, Forces, Energy, Momentum, Circular Motion</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[20px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Thermodynamics</h3><span class=\"bg-[#eff6ff] text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-[6px] shrink-0 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">LIVE</span></div><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed mt-auto\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Conservation Laws, Heat Transfer, Entropy, Gas Laws</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[20px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Waves &amp; Optics</h3><span class=\"bg-[#eff6ff] text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-[6px] shrink-0 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">LIVE</span></div><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed mt-auto\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Transverse Waves, Sound, Light, Interference, Doppler</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[20px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Electromagnetism</h3><span class=\"bg-[#eff6ff] text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-[6px] shrink-0 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">LIVE</span></div><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed mt-auto\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Electric Fields, Circuits, Magnetism, Magnetic Forces</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[20px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Modern Physics</h3><span class=\"bg-[#eff6ff] text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-[6px] shrink-0 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">LIVE</span></div><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed mt-auto\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">Special Relativity, Quantum Mechanics, Nuclear, Radioactivity</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[20px] p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-slate-200 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-100\" style=\"box-shadow:0 10px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:700;color:rgb(15, 23, 42)\">Kinematics</h3><span class=\"bg-[#eff6ff] text-blue-500 text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-[6px] shrink-0 uppercase\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">LIVE</span></div><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed mt-auto\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(100, 116, 139)\">SUVAT Equations, Velocity, Acceleration, Graphs of Motion</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-medium text-[15px] px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-transparent hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all duration-300 group\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"#\">See full roadmap<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></section><section id=\"waitlist\" class=\"py-24 bg-[#0a0f1e] my-[40px] relative\"><div class=\"max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20 flex flex-col items-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-size:12px;color:rgb(59, 130, 246)\">COMING SOON</span><h2 class=\"text-[clamp(40px,5vw,60px)] leading-[1.05]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-instrument-serif);font-weight:400;color:rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Everything you need to master<br class=\"hidden md:block\"/> physics fundamentals</h2></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8 mb-20\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-[18px] h-[18px] text-[#3b82f6] shrink-0 mt-[4px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[16px] leading-[28px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(226, 232, 240)\">Comprehensive lessons on all core physics topics</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-[18px] h-[18px] text-[#3b82f6] shrink-0 mt-[4px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[16px] leading-[28px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(226, 232, 240)\">1,000+ practice problems with full solutions</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-[18px] h-[18px] text-[#3b82f6] shrink-0 mt-[4px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[16px] leading-[28px]\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans);font-weight:400;color:rgb(226, 232, 240)\">Formula sheets and quick-reference guides</span></div><div class=\"flex items-star