cle, topic, author, and resource — all in one place for easy discovery.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-[20px] bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h3 class=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\">All Articles</h3><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px] text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 mt-0.5\">•</span> <span class=\"leading-[1.5]\">Newton&#x27;s Laws of Motion</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px] text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 mt-0.5\">•</span> <span class=\"leading-[1.5]\">Newton&#x27;s Second Law (F=ma)</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px] text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 mt-0.5\">•</span> <span class=\"leading-[1.5]\">Transverse Waves Explained</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px] text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 mt-0.5\">•</span> <span class=\"leading-[1.5]\">What Is Energy?</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px] text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-dm-sans)\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 mt-0.5\">•</span> <span class=\"leading-[1.5]\">Projectile Motion: Complete Guide</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-[14px] text-slate-500 hover:text-bl